Executive Profile
Laura J. Sloate CFAManaging Director, Neuberger Berman BD LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.----
Background

		Ms. Laura J. Sloate is currently employed at Neuberger Berman, LLC. She was previously the Chairman, Treasurer, Chief Investment Officer, and Director of Research at Sloate Weisman. Prior to co-founding Sloate Weisman in 1974, Ms. Sloate had been employed at Neuberger Berman and Drexel, Burham. She began her career in 1968 as a Security Analyst at Scheinman, Hochstin & Trotta. Ms. Sloate is active with the Metropolitan Opera Association and Central Synagogue, and is ... a member of the Board of Directors of the Richard Tucker Music Foundation. She is also a Member of the New York Society of Security Analysts. Ms. Sloate received her bachelor's degree from Barnard and her master's degree from Columbia. She is a C.F.A. charter holder.Read Full Background




